extends layout
block style
  link(rel='stylesheet', href='./style/manual.css')
block content
  .container.content
    .headline-center-v2.headline-center-v2-dark.margin-bottom-60
      h2 保養須知
      span.bordered-icon
        img(src='./img/bricon.png')

    .row.margin-bottom-20.container(style="display: flex; align-items: center;")
      .col-sm-2(style="margin-right: 3rem;")
        img(src="https://i.imgur.com/90VdaM7.png", style="width: 150px")
      .col-sm-8
        p 若有局部污漬、殘膠，請以布沾環保去漬油輕微擦拭污漬處。
    .row.margin-bottom-20.container(style="display: flex; align-items: center;")
      .col-sm-2(style="margin-right: 3rem;")
        img(src="https://i.imgur.com/AL9fnY3.png", style="width: 150px")
      .col-sm-8
        p 請勿使用甲苯、去光水或去標籤劑擦拭，會造成箱殼受損。
    .row.margin-bottom-20.container(style="display: flex; align-items: center;")
      .col-sm-2(style="margin-right: 3rem;")
        img(src="https://i.imgur.com/qN6cowl.png", style="width: 150px")
      .col-sm-8
        p 若發現輪子有不順的情況，可以上適當的潤滑油使輪子更順暢、使用更持久。
